## ðŸ”¹ Raspberry Pi Pico

The **Raspberry Pi Pico** is a compact, cost-effective microcontroller board designed for embedded applications.

**Key Specifications:**

- **Microcontroller:** RP2040 (Dual-core Arm Cortex-M0+ @ up to 133 MHz)
- **Memory:** 264 KB SRAM
- **Flash Storage:** 2 MB onboard QSPI Flash
- **GPIO Pins:** 26 multi-function GPIOs (3 analog inputs)
- **Interfaces:** 2Ã— SPI, 2Ã— I2C, 2Ã— UART, 16Ã— PWM channels
- **USB:** USB 1.1 Host and Device support
- **Power Input:** 1.8V to 5.5V DC
- **Dimensions:** 21 mm Ã— 51 mm
- **Programming Support:** C/C++ and MicroPython ([Raspberry Pi Pico W](https://robu.in/product/raspberry-pi-pico-w/?utm_source=chatgpt.com), [Raspberry Pi Pico W Pinout, Projects & Spec - devboards.info](https://devboards.info/boards/raspberry-pi-pico-w?utm_source=chatgpt.com), [Raspberry Pi Pico W and Pico WH - Thingbits India](https://www.thingbits.in/products/raspberry-pi-pico-w?utm_source=chatgpt.com), [Raspberry Pi Pico W - About - DomoticX](https://domoticx.net/docs/raspberry-pi-pico-w-about/?utm_source=chatgpt.com))

